  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      single-center study carried out in order to evaluate in prospective among patients seen or
      treated in the pediatric endocrinology unit and multidisciplinary management of obesity, the
      potential number of patients eligible for surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a feasibility study in order to file a subsequent national project as part of a PHRC
      on bariatric surgery in adolescents.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
